{"tid":2404132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位香港人，大家喺支那全速推動殖民嘅香港撐得住嘛？","createTime":"2021-02-11T13:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T17:48:23.000Z","uid":131691,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"98271f185c2994bd286bf9674b5bc3180f966d2e","tid":2404132,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"安心出殯全速前進（食肆只係第一步，中国係入商場入屋苑都會trace）<br />\n強迫中国籍全速前進（禁用bno只係第一步）<br />\n洗腦教育全速前進（經濟都要愛國，有中国特色嘅生物學，哈哈）<br />\n消滅廣東話全速前進（取消廣東話口試只係第一步，廣東省嘅學校係會校規禁止學生講廣東話）<br />\n強迫升旗全速前進（話光復旗同藍白旗係犯法只係第一步）<br />\n強迫宣誓全速前進（公務員只係第一步）<br />\n<br />\n香港現正被殖民，請問有幾多香港人會選擇服從，有幾多香港人會選擇逃避，有幾多香港人會選擇為香港而繼續做香港人？<br />\n<br />\n各位撐住呀。"},{"pid":"60ca2e0d30332eb722687201f9db25cf5a4aba21","tid":2404132,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9193869d63779fef0b278dcb0887712ee953905","tid":2404132,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"撑住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b765be258bdc277399dd41e061d06bb2ba5122ec","tid":2404132,"uid":64092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做好香港人"},{"pid":"774cfbc7a200d8b62f1d2d566d0571b76c8be5e8","tid":2404132,"uid":218158,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">香港獨立、唯一出路！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港、時代革命<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"175d8fb6454b10a1bb180cb3355f95824fc73e65","tid":2404132,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">香港現正被殖民</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n單程證&amp;雙飛開始就殖緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmo